{"code":0,"msg":"ok","data":{"article":{"authorCode":"admin","authorName":"孙天骁","classify":"文学类","content":"<p class=\"ql-align-center\">如果有一天，</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">熟悉的人变得陌生。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你开始感觉他思维古板，</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你开始嘲笑他不求甚解。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你感觉他活得像十年前的自己，</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">目光短浅，毫无长进。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">如果有一天，</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">陌生的人变得熟悉。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你开始感觉他品位斐然，</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你开始品味他细致随和。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你感觉他活得像预想中的自己，</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">随性自如，饱读诗书。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">如果有一天，</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">熟悉的人变得陌生。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你开始感觉她不知前沿，</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你开始嘲笑她故步自封。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你感觉她活得蛮因循守旧。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">日复一日，重复劳动。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">如果有一天，</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">陌生的人变得熟悉。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你开始感觉她眼光真诚，</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你开始感觉她知性智慧。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你感觉她活得蛮轻松有趣，</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">别出心裁，惬意满园。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">熟悉 VS 陌生</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">但不要忘记陌生的人我们曾经熟悉过</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">熟悉的人也有可能会再变得陌生起来</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">我有一天，会参透人际交往的规律和套路</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">谈笑风生，闲适自如。</p>","createTime":"2020-03-01 21:24:21","customCoverKey":"","id":260,"isGood":false,"isTop":false,"publicState":0,"replyCount":3,"state":0,"tags":["诗歌"],"title":"熟悉 VS 陌生","urlCode":"EX81N3PO9R","viewCount":165,"viewGroup":-1,"authPassed":true},"author":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙